			</span><br />
			<span class="gensmall">Downloaded 19 times</span>
		

		<br />
	</div><br /><br />Both controllers act the same, only &quot;B&quot; button is working fine, other buttons are not working at all. The strange thing is - when I hold the B button, im able to use left, right, start, select and A buttons - I wonder if schematics found on the web are correct, or maybe I made some mistakes while designing that simple boards. I have already build an arcade controller for NES and Sega MD without bigger issues.<br /><br />Looking forward for some help!</div>

